tic monopoles, a space- charge vacuum current in\naddition to the displacement current, models of the leptons having an internal\nvortex-like structure and force balance, photon models with a small but nonzero\nrest mass and a slightly reduced velocity of propagation, and particle-wave\nproperties, explaining self-interference even of single electrons or photons.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 11 Dec 2001 14:51:36 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sat, 12 Jan 2002 11:52:40 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Fri, 15 Feb 2002 14:25:36 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Thu, 14 Mar 2002 10:41:14 GMT"},{"version":"v5","created":"Mon, 19 Apr 2004 12:39:08 GMT"},{"version":"v6","created":"Fri, 25 Jun 2004 19:54:34 GMT"},{"version":"v7","created":"Thu, 1 Sep 2005 14:57:22 GMT"}],"update_date":"2007-05-23"}
